            <div>
                <opener>
                    <salute>Dear Sir</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>The inclosed will inform you that the box with the <bibl type="authorial">
                        <title ref="bidb.xml#bi0013">2d part of the Tour</title>
                    </bibl>
                    was sent this week to <placeName ref="pldb.xml#pl0758">your house in Town</placeName>. <persName ref="pe0014">Moses</persName>
                    will soon form a bill &amp; hopes the whole will meet <choice>
                        <abbr>y<hi rend="superscript">y</hi>
                        </abbr>
                        <expan>your</expan>
                    </choice>
                    approbation. The <bibl type="authorial">
                        <title ref="bidb.xml#bi0012">first part</title>
                    </bibl> came safe: &amp; shall ne
                    returned at Christmas. a beginning is made to <bibl type="authorial">
                        <title ref="bidb.xml#bi0032">the journey to London</title>
                    </bibl>. The weather
                        in these parts is dreadful &amp; must add to our calamities. I am</p>
                <closer>Dear Sir
                    <lb/>
                    <choice>
                        <abbr>Y<hi rend="superscript">y</hi> affect:</abbr>
                        <expan>Your affectionate</expan>
                    </choice> humble <choice>
                        <abbr>Serv<hi rend="superscript">t</hi>
                        </abbr>
                        <expan>Servant</expan>
                    </choice>
                    <signed>
                        <persName ref="pe0232">
                            <choice>
                                <abbr>Tho.</abbr>
                                <expan>Thomas</expan>
                            </choice> Pennant</persName>
                    </signed>
                    <dateline>
                        <placeName ref="pldb.xml#pl0001">Downing</placeName> <choice>
                            <abbr>Aug.</abbr>
                            <expan>August</expan>
                        </choice> 16 <hi rend="superscript">th</hi> 1782.</dateline>
                </closer>
                </div>
            <div>
                <p>
                    <add place="margin">17:6
                    <lb/>17:6
                    <lb/>17:6
                    <lb/>17:6.
                    <lb/>17:6.
                    <lb/>4:7:6</add>
